      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=blm2eub23d]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=blm2eub23d]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=d3duvn5sdv]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=d3duvn5sdv]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=kh9kworj0y]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=kh9kworj0y]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"blm2eub23d\">Resource</span></strong>: HDRI</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"d3duvn5sdv\">Captured by</span></strong>: <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://aversten.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Peter Aversten</a></p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"kh9kworj0y\">Use</span></strong>: Attach this map to a PxrDomeLight</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://assets.renderman.pixar.com/resources/berns_red_room_hdri/4557_bernsredroomhdr.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469073/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285298014&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608469073/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285298014&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608469101\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"b